      <ul>
        <li><strong>Legal name:</strong> SyncAgency LLC</li>
        <li><strong>Managing member:</strong> Lucas Provenzano (Sole Member)</li>
        <li><strong>EIN:</strong> 35-2955550</li>
        <li><strong>Registered office:</strong> 1209 Mountain Rd Pl NE Ste H, Albuquerque, NM 87110, United States</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@syncagency.fr">contact@syncagency.fr</a></li>
        <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://www.syncagency.fr">https://www.syncagency.fr</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider" />

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">2. Definitions</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>"Service"</strong> means the SyncAgency platform, its features, and the associated software.</li>
        <li><strong>"User"</strong> means any individual or legal entity accessing the Service.</li>
        <li><strong>"Account"</strong> means the personal space created by the User to access the Service.</li>
        <li><strong>"Agency"</strong> means the business entity registered on the platform, which may associate multiple team members and models.</li>
        <li><strong>"Data"</strong> means all information transmitted or generated by the User in connection with the use of the Service.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider" />

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">3. Access to the Service and Account Creation</h2>
      <p>Access to the Service requires the creation of an account. The User agrees to provide accurate and complete information and to keep it up to date.</p>
