    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider" />

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">4. Description of the Service</h2>
      <p>SyncAgency is a CRM (Customer Relationship Management) software offered as SaaS, intended for agencies managing content creators operating on messaging platforms such as Telegram and WhatsApp. The Service notably includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Centralization of Telegram and WhatsApp conversations in a unified interface;</li>
        <li>Management of a media and script library per model (Vault);</li>
        <li>A bulk messaging module (Mass DM) with segmentation;</li>
        <li>An integrated payment processor allowing payments to be received directly within conversations;</li>
        <li>Performance tracking dashboards for chatter teams;</li>
        <li>A marketing acquisition module (depending on the subscribed plan) including social media account tracking and tracking link management;</li>
        <li>A real-time notification system.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>The available features depend on the subscription plan chosen by the User. SyncAgency reserves the right to modify, add, or remove features at any time, subject to reasonable notice.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider" />

    <div class="legal-section">
