      <p>The User agrees to use the Service in a lawful, fair manner and in compliance with these Terms of Use. In particular, it is prohibited to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the Service for unlawful, fraudulent purposes or purposes contrary to public order;</li>
        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to the systems, data, or accounts of other users;</li>
        <li>Introduce viruses, malware, or any harmful code into the Service;</li>
        <li>Reproduce, copy, resell, or commercially exploit all or part of the Service without SyncAgency's prior written authorization;</li>
        <li>Automate access to the Service through unauthorized bots or scripts;</li>
        <li>Send unsolicited communications (spam) through the Service's features;</li>
        <li>Collect personal data of third parties without their consent.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>The User is solely responsible for the content they send, publish, or transmit through the Service, as well as for the consequences of such transmissions toward third parties.</p>
