    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider" />

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">7. Availability and Maintenance</h2>
      <p>SyncAgency endeavors to keep the Service available 24/7. However, interruptions may occur due to maintenance, updates, or technical incidents beyond SyncAgency's control.</p>
      <p>SyncAgency undertakes to inform Users of scheduled maintenance with reasonable notice. In the event of an unforeseen interruption, SyncAgency does everything possible to restore the Service as quickly as possible.</p>
      <p>SyncAgency cannot be held liable for any unavailability of the Service due to external causes (internet outages, force majeure, failures of third-party platforms such as Telegram or WhatsApp).</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider" />

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>To the extent permitted by applicable law, SyncAgency shall not be liable for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages resulting from the use of or inability to use the Service;</li>
        <li>Loss of data due to User conduct or to circumstances beyond SyncAgency's control;</li>
        <li>Any harm resulting from the use of third-party platforms integrated into the Service (Telegram, WhatsApp, etc.);</li>
