    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">10. Term, Termination, and Suspension</h2>
      <p>These Terms of Use are entered into for an indefinite term as of the creation of the Account by the User.</p>
      <p>The User may terminate their account at any time from the settings of their personal space or by contacting SyncAgency at <a href="mailto:contact@syncagency.fr">contact@syncagency.fr</a>. Termination takes effect at the end of the current billing period.</p>
      <p>SyncAgency reserves the right to suspend or terminate a User's access in the event of a breach of these Terms of Use, without prejudice to any claim for damages.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider" />

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">11. Changes to the Terms of Use</h2>
      <p>SyncAgency reserves the right to modify these Terms of Use at any time. Changes are notified to Users by email or via an in-app notification, with a minimum notice period of 15 days before they take effect.</p>
      <p>Continued use of the Service after the effective date of the new Terms of Use constitutes acceptance of them. In the event of refusal, the User may terminate their account in accordance with Section 10.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider" />

